data.description: SELLER OFFERING Special 10K CONCESSION towards rate buy down with approved contract! Welcome to this amazing townhome listing located in a vibrant community, offering a plethora of amenities and conveniently located near some of the best attractions in town. This townhome truly offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful retreat with all the excitement just moments away.Home has brand new carpet and fresh paint. Tiled master shower with garden tub. Master walk in closet is huge. Enjoy cooking in the kitchen while hosting your guest in the great room. High ceiling makes this place seem even larger than it is. One of the highlights of this community is the sparkling swimming pool. Whether you want to take a refreshing dip on a hot summer day or simply lounge by the poolside, this amenity provides the perfect place to relax and enjoy the sunshine.For those who love outdoor activities, the community also features fishing ponds, allowing you to cast your line and enjoy some quality time connecting with nature. Imagine spending a lazy afternoon fishing and soaking up the tranquility of your surroundings.Located right across the street from Arnold High School, this townhome offers a convenient location for families with school-aged children. This close proximity ensures a hassle-free commute, making it easy for students to attend classes and extracurricular activities.In addition to being near the high school, this townhome is also just a short distance from the pier and Shipwreck Island Waterpark. Spend weekends enjoying thrilling water slides and lazy river rides, or explore the vibrant local pier with its bustling atmosphere and stunning views.With its ideal location, this townhome allows you to experience the best of coastal living. Enjoy the convenience of being close to dining options, shopping centers, and other local attractions, while still having a peaceful and comfortable place to call home.Don't miss out on the opportunity to live in this fantastic townhome and experience the amazing amenities and attractions that surround it. Schedule a showing today and see for yourself why this property is perfect for you. New carpet and fresh paint.
